# Responsive Sizing Rules

**MANDATORY**: All UI components must use responsive Tailwind classes to scale appropriately across screen sizes.

## Text Sizes

| Element | Classes |
|---------|---------|
| Page title (h1) | `text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl xl:text-5xl` |
| Section title (h2) | `text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl` |
| Card title (h3) | `text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl xl:text-2xl` |
| Body text | `text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg` |
| Small text | `text-xs sm:text-sm lg:text-base` |
| Tiny/label text | `text-[10px] sm:text-xs lg:text-sm` |

## Spacing

| Size | Classes |
|------|---------|
| Large | `p-4 sm:p-6 lg:p-8 xl:p-10` |
| Medium | `p-3 sm:p-4 lg:p-5 xl:p-6` |
| Small | `p-2 sm:p-3 lg:p-4` |
| Gaps | `gap-2 sm:gap-3 lg:gap-4` or `gap-3 sm:gap-4 lg:gap-5` |

## Icons

| Size | Classes |
|------|---------|
| Large | `w-5 h-5 sm:w-6 sm:h-6 lg:w-7 lg:h-7` |
| Medium | `w-4 h-4 sm:w-5 sm:h-5 lg:w-6 lg:h-6` |
| Small | `w-3.5 h-3.5 sm:w-4 sm:h-4 lg:w-5 lg:h-5` |

## Buttons

```tsx
// Height + padding scale together
className="h-8 sm:h-9 lg:h-10 xl:h-11 px-3 sm:px-4 lg:px-5 text-xs sm:text-sm lg:text-base"
```

## Cards & Containers

```tsx
// Padding
className="p-3 sm:p-4 lg:p-5 xl:p-6"

// Border radius (larger elements)
className="rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl"
```

## Avatars

| Size | Classes |
|------|---------|
| Large | `w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 lg:w-16 lg:h-16` |
| Medium | `w-8 h-8 sm:w-10 sm:h-10 lg:w-12 lg:h-12` |
| Small | `w-6 h-6 sm:w-8 sm:h-8` |

## Exceptions (No responsive needed)

- Layout utilities: `flex`, `grid`, `hidden`, `block`
- Colors: `bg-*`, `text-*` (color only)
- Borders: `border`, `border-*`
- Very small fixed elements (2-4px)
- Elements inside already-scaled containers

## Bad vs Good Examples

```tsx
// ❌ BAD - Static sizing
<h1 className="text-3xl font-bold">Title</h1>
<div className="p-6">Content</div>
<button className="h-10 px-6 text-sm">Click</button>

// ✅ GOOD - Responsive sizing
<h1 className="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold">Title</h1>
<div className="p-4 sm:p-5 lg:p-6">Content</div>
<button className="h-8 sm:h-9 lg:h-10 px-4 sm:px-5 lg:px-6 text-xs sm:text-sm lg:text-base">Click</button>
```

## Checklist for New Components

- [ ] Page/section titles have responsive text sizes
- [ ] Body text scales appropriately
- [ ] Container padding is responsive
- [ ] Gaps/margins scale with screen size
- [ ] Buttons have responsive height, padding, and text
- [ ] Icons scale with their containers
- [ ] Border radius scales on larger elements
